title: RubyMine 6.3.2 Build 135.809
description:
JetBrains RubyMine is a commercial IDE for Ruby and Ruby on Rails built on JetBrains' IntelliJ IDEA platform.

RubyMine provides intelligent code completion for Ruby and Ruby on Rails code, on-the-fly code analysis and refactoring support for both plain Ruby projects and web applications built with Ruby on Rails.

Install then use the keygen.
